{"tid":1383051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[很重要]無論聽日成功與否，請勿被帶風向互相攻擊﹗﹗","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T23:38:13.000Z","uid":229880,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"62a340218d447c3f3dc86cd209b99921a6144899","tid":1383051,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"今日國務院出黎講左40分鐘無內容嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然好多專業嘅巴打都分析左，中國打緊貿易戰，緊係唔想上身<br />\n同時踢返個波俾777<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係，中國人就係有鋪干涉別人嘅心癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因此，好相信李思嫣之流，係水到後就會走返出黎，<br />\n另又會有一大堆1毛、3毛、5毛黎洗版帶風向<br />\n<br />\n假如我地聽朝塞交通唔夠noise，就一定會引我地罵戰<br />\n亦會引風向去接受1至2個訴求就應該收手等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，聽朝無論係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n<strong>請各位都唔好俾人引戰</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6c855c276929c80f43e0101957801041bb4978","tid":1383051,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3506908569d63df05ec19e727d3fa1017e2d69d7","tid":1383051,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime